data.description: Discover the allure of Jungle Terrace! Presenting a captivating 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-family home that is ready for immediate occupancy. Rest assured, this residence is safely nestled outside the flood zone, boasting a secure flood code of X.    Embrace the convenience of a fully fenced backyard—an ideal space for your furry friends to roam freely. Inside, the home boasts a seamless expanse of tile flooring, a dedicated laundry room, and a stylish kitchen featuring granite countertops paired with modern appliances.    Luxuriate in the master bathroom's inviting shower and unwind in the comfort of a tub in the second bathroom. Beyond the comforts of home, this property positions you mere minutes away from shopping, grocery stores, a short 15-minute drive from Downtown, less than 5 minutes from Tyrone Mall and a quick 10-minute commute to the beaches.    Seize the opportunity to experience this residence firsthand—where every detail speaks of ease and style. Envision the possibilities, and transform this house into your cherished home. Don't miss the chance; schedule your visit today!
